Class PopulateClientStorageLoadContext<InboundMessageType,OutboundMessageType>

    Component, DestructableComponent, InitializableComponent, ProfileAction<InboundMessageType,OutboundMessageType>

    public class PopulateClientStorageLoadContext<InboundMessageType,OutboundMessageType>
extends AbstractProfileAction<InboundMessageType,OutboundMessageType>
    An action that creates and populates a ClientStorageLoadContext with any storage keys identified as missing from the current session and in need of loading.

    The action will signal the LOAD_NOT_NEEDED event if it is unnecessary to proceed with the load operation.

    Event:
    EventIds.PROCEED_EVENT_ID, LOAD_NOT_NEEDED
